  "description": "Celebrate with the ultimate Lake Travis bachelorette party boat cruise in Austin at Premier Party Cruises. Our ATX Disco Cruise offers three time slots to fit your schedule: Friday afternoons at $95/person, Saturday mornings at $105/person, and Saturday evenings at $85/person. Every bachelorette party cruise features a 4-hour Lake Travis experience with professional DJ, professional photographer capturing Instagram-worthy moments, BYOB cooler setup with ice, giant lily pad floats, party decorations, and an amazing party atmosphere with other bachelorette groups. Perfect for groups of 20-40+ guests. Also available: private boat rentals for intimate celebrations ranging from 14-75 person capacity.",
